channel.title: Web Client
channel.description:
I recently decided to start my own RSC for me and my friends. I have the server running fine, but web client won't work here is my error:
It get's stuck at "Downloading files, please wait."
When I run it from my local machine I get this error:
[code][java] Trying http://elitewow.game-host.org/forums/cache/ => Unable to obtain file.[/code]
See for yourself at: elitewow.game-host.org/webclient.html
